---
title: Blackened Chicken & Cauliflower Grits with Lemon Pan Sauce & Roasted Green Beans
description: Grits are a Southern staple, but the classic side gets a health-nut twist tonight. Enter: Cauliflower grits. Granules of cauliflower rice take on the flavor of blackening spices with a texture that’s reminiscent of traditional grits. Our chefs also put the same seasoning on tonight’s chicken, because everything on the plate deserves a little Southern-style heat. A lemon pan sauce and green beans round out the meal. Fix a plate and start pillin’ on the goodness!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/blackened-chicken-cauliflower-grits-f47bbb42.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/blackened-chicken-cauliflower-grits-61670b773a460a530721239c-b9969e32.pdf
servings: 2
time required: 25 minutes
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 530 kcal
  fat: 33 g
  saturated fat: 16 g
  carbohydrates: 23 g
  sugar: 9 g
